  public static final String CONST_INCH_TEAM_ITEM_DES1 ="Anton co-founded the 1inch Network in May 2019. With over seven years of blockchain development and engineering experience, he believes he can help build a better future for DeFi. Before starting 1inch, he gained blockchain development experience at projects like Near Protocol. He graduated from the Institute of Cryptography, Telecommunications and Computer Science in 2011, majoring in computer science. ";
  public static final String CONST_INCH_TEAM_ITEM_DES2 ="Sergej brought his 11 years of experience as a software engineer to co-found the 1inch Network in 2019. Before starting at 1inch, he worked as software engineer for Porsche AG, as CEO at Mimacom AG and Bulktrade GmbH. His specialisation and in-depth knowledge in development have given the 1inch Network a solid foundation. ";
  public static final String CONST_INCH_TEAM_ITEM_DES3 ="Sergey is an experienced marketing communications professional with over 15 years of leading global PR and media strategy for a variety of companies ranging from multi million funded IT startups to top leading media companies in Russia. He’s experienced in media relations, digital marketing, journalism, editing and analyzing large volumes of data. He’s also skilled in building networks and stakeholder management.";
  public static final String CONST_INCH_TEAM_ITEM_DES4 ="Nikita has served multiple roles in his career, including Chief Financial Officer, Market Research Analyst and Head of Business Development. With his combined experience, he’s been working as the Chief Business Development Officer of the 1inch Network since 2020. He holds a master of science, majoring in Finance and Investment at the Nottingham University Business School.";
  public static final String CONST_INCH_TEAM_ITEM_DES5 ="Natalia is the Support and Community Lead at the 1inch Network. Before joining the team, she worked as a Content and Communication Assistant and Community Manager for STOKR and Token Engineering Global Gathering TEGG 2019. She holds two master's degrees in Philosophy and Political Science.";
  public static final String CONST_INCH_TEAM_ITEM_DES6 ="Vitalii is a professional artist and designer with over 13 years of experience in UI design, motion design, illustrations and 3D CGI. He has been leading the 1inch Network’s design team since 2020. Vitalii graduated from the School of Arts with honors.";
  public static final String CONST_INCH_TEAM_ITEM_DES7 ="With over ten years of experience in Web and UI design, Pavel started working with the 1inch Network in 2020. He holds a master's degree in Computer Software Engineering from the Kherson State University.";
  public static final String CONST_INCH_TEAM_ITEM_DES8 ="Anastasia has worked as a banking and business development manager for over six years, where she was in charge of the banking inquiries, KYC processes and bank payment transfers. She’s now brought her experiences to help manage funds at the 1inch Network. She graduated from Ural State Pedagogical University.";

  public static final String CONST_INCH_FAQ_CONTENT1 ="The 1inch Network has always paid special attention to security issues, using the most advanced protection methods. 1inch performs regular smart contract audits to discover possible vulnerabilities. They also make sure the smart contracts are unupgradable by design, so no one can access the smart contracts’ code and, consequently, to funds locked in them. DEX aggregators, like 1inch, unite all of these exchanges in one place, enabling users to trade without having to provide access to funds in their wallets to anyone. Therefore, if a DEX has vulnerabilities, 1inch can protect users from them.";
